mmunication and we show that unlike dense\ncoding with two-qubit random states, senders' operations are always helpful to\nprobabilistically enhance the capabilities of implementing dense coding as well\nas teleportation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 18:22:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2021 20:50:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-24"}
