\nof these four multiplets. We also identify an interesting possible connection\nbetween the smallness of the neutrino masses and a helicity suppression of the\nPati-Salam limits for three of the four multiplets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 21:05:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 May 2021 05:43:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-01"}
