ic speeches in both verbal and non-verbal\ndomain with the computational power of a neural network to design a fair\nprediction system for speakers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2020 06:36:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 20:48:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 04:59:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-17"}
